Confirm zero regressions: filters remain exact, scroll position restores to the same
row (not just "close"), and the URL correctly reflects state on browser back/forward.
Fix anything that breaks before proceeding to Week 8 — this pattern gets reused
everywhere from here on, so bugs here compound.
```

